http://www.isid.org

[1]
Date: Fri 14 Aug 2015
Source: Associated Press [edited]
http://www.whas11.com/story/news/local/indiana/2015/08/14/ind-health-dept-reports-3-e-coli/31758163/


The Indiana State Department of Health says its staff have confirmed that 3 people have been infected with _Escherichia coli_. The confirmation, on Friday 14 Aug 2015, comes as the department investigates reports of diarrheal illness in 3 Indiana counties. Health Department officials say the agency is working with public health officials in Fulton, Wabash, and Marshall counties to determine the cause of illness in the 3 other individuals. The 6 cases currently known include 1 death.

Officials say family members and others who may have been in contact with the 6 are being monitored for diarrheal illness.

